<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shut-v">shut <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ʃʌt/    美 /ʃʌt/  </p>
<p>(shut, shut)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi 关上；闭上；合上：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>shut</strong> one’s <strong>eyes</strong> / a book
闭上眼睛/合上书</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The window won’t shut.
这扇窗户关不上。</p></div>

<h4 id="2vt">2.<strong>vt 禁闭；把...关住：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They shut the poor girl in the room upstairs.
他们把那可怜的女孩关在楼上的房间里。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-vt-vi-close">3.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (使) 停止营业(close)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s time to shut the shop.
商店该关门了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The stores shut at 9:30 pm.
这些商店晚上9:30关门。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="shut-down">shut down</h3>
<p>1.<strong>关闭 (工厂等)；使 (机器、装置等) 停止运转：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Parents in Glasgow are reacting against the plan to shut down 25 primary schools.
在格拉斯哥，父母们反对关闭25所小学的计划。</p><footer>2009 湖北改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>shut down the computer system
关闭计算机系统</p></div>

<h3 id="shut-in">shut in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>把…关在房内</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="shut-off">shut off</h3>
<p>1.<strong>关掉；切断 (turn off)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t forget to shut off the water supply.
别忘了关闭供水系统。</p></div>

<h3 id="shut-out-of">shut out (of)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使…不能进入；挡住；不去想：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sunglasses shut out 99 percent of the sun’s harmful rays.
太阳镜能遮挡99%的太阳光中的有害射线。</p></div>

<h3 id="shut-up">shut up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>关闭；(使) 住口：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Shut up the window before you go out.
出去前关好窗户。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tell him to shut up.
叫他住嘴。</p></div></div>